===Squad stats===
[[Image:VÃ­ctor ValdÃ©s - 001.jpg|right|thumb|150px|[[VÃ­ctor ValdÃ©s]] has the most starts in this season.]]

[[VÃ­ctor ValdÃ©s]] and [[Ãric Abidal]] have been the only two players that have started all the matches (excepting [[Copa Catalunya]], when Barcelona didn't use the same players as for the other competitions). Previously, [[Gianluca Zambrotta]] and [[Yaya TourÃ©]] started all the matches until they got injured. [[Oleguer Presas]] replaced Zambrotta and [[AndrÃ©s Iniesta]] replaced TourÃ©. [[Giovani Dos Santos|Giovani dos Santos]] and [[Bojan KrkiÄ|Bojan]] were the substitute forwards, while [[Santiago Ezquerro]] played only in the [[Copa Catalunya]], as well as [[EiÃ°ur GuÃ°johnsen]] playing once. [[Thierry Henry]] started the majority of the matches when [[Samuel Eto'o]] got injured. He scored his first [[Hat-trick#Association football|hat trick]] wearing BarÃ§a's jersey, and he's the second goal scorer with four goals. [[Ronaldinho]] missed three matches due to an injury.<ref>[http://www.fcbarcelona.cat/web/english/noticies/futbol/temporada07-08/09/n070922101084.html FCBarcelona.cat: Ronaldinho to miss Sevilla match]</ref> The most outstanding player has been [[Lionel Messi]] with eight goals in nine appearances. He is the top scorer at the moment.<br />
