==Club==
===Coaching staff===
[[Image:Frank Rijkaard (2007).jpg|right|thumb|100px|[[Frank Rijkaard]], managing Barcelona since 2003.]]

This season will be the fifth consecutive season for [[Frank Rijkaard]] as FC Barcelona's manager<ref>[http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=FC_Barcelona&oldid=164100883#Recent_seasons en.wikipedia.org: FC Barcelona on 12 October 2007]</ref>. Even though BarÃ§a didn't win any major competition last season<ref>[[2006-07 FC Barcelona season#Competitions|2006-07 FC Barcelona season]]</ref>, the president [[Joan Laporta]] confirmed his presence for this season<ref>[http://www.fcbarcelona.cat/web/english/noticies/futbol/temporada06-07/06/n070619100998.html FCBarcelona.cat: Changes on the way]</ref>. All staff from last season, except doctor Gil Rodas, are remaining<ref>[[2006-07 FC Barcelona season#Coaching staff|2006-07 FC Barcelona season]]</ref>.<br />
