==Competitions==
===Overall===
As in nine out of the last ten seasons<ref>[http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=FC_Barcelona&oldid=165116141#Recent_seasons en.wikipedia.org: FC Barcelona on 17 October 2007]</ref>, FC Barcelona is going to be present in all major competitions this season. [[La Liga 2007-08|First division]], [[Copa del Rey 2007-08|Copa del Rey]] in [[Spain]] and [[UEFA Champions League 2007-08|UEFA Champions League]] in [[Europe]]. Also, [[Copa Catalunya]] in BarÃ§a's native [[Autonomous Community|autonomous community]] of [[Catalonia]], but using mostly [[FC Barcelona B]]'s players (see matches' reports). Their goal, set at the start of the season, is to win all the possible trophies.<ref>[http://www.fcbarcelona.cat/web/english/noticies/futbol/temporada07-08/07/n070722101346.html FCBarcelona.cat: Xavi: "We aim to win everything"]</ref><ref>[http://www.fcbarcelona.cat/web/english/noticies/futbol/temporada07-08/07/n070720101328.html FCBarcelona.cat: "BarÃ§a will fight to win everything"]</ref> So far, they ended as runner-ups in the less important [[Copa Catalunya]].<br />
